The probabilistic LDA model [23] can be utilized to estimate K microbial assemblages from a human gut metagenomic dataset, where K is a given parameter. Let the numbers of individuals (samples) and genera be denoted by N and D, respectively. In the LDA model, the ith metagenome sample (i∈{1,...,N}) has a categorical distribution with parameter \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
