				\begin{document}$\theta _{i}=\{\theta _{i,k}\}_{k=1}^{K}$\end{document}θi={θi,k}k=1K over microbial assemblages where θi,k is the occurrence probability of the kth assemblage in the ith sample. The kth microbial assemblage has a categorical distribution with parameter \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
